column1: This COVID-19 pandemic was unnecessarily worsened by China's recklessness. Congressman Tiffany knows we must hold the communist Chinese government accountable and no longer be complacent towards the country’s misdeeds that led to this. -staff

Tricia Zunker is the leader of a group trying to use the COVID-19 pandemic as a reason to release dangerous criminals from prison and back into our communities. Zunker’s group should not be taking advantage of this public health crisis to further its own political agenda. -staff

Tom’s top priority is providing Wisconsin families with the bridge necessary to safely get us through the COVID-19 pandemic and back to prosperity. That’s why he voted for the emergency COVID-19 legislation to protect Wisconsinites during this public health emergency. -staff

Tom will fight to  ✅Get WI families through the COVID-19 pandemic & back to prosperity. ✅Stop the spread of socialism & protect the American dream. ✅Lower healthcare cost & increase access. ✅Secure free & fair trade deals for WI farmers. ✅Delist gray wolf -staff

I joined @DrydenWire today for a discussion on coronavirus the new order from Gov. Evers how this affects our campaign and more. Watch our interview here → https://t.co/cpnm5vRW7I

Today is Certified Nurses Day and we honor the men and women who work so hard to keep us healthy. Thank you for all you do every day — but especially now as you put in extra long days to help us fight coronavirus.
